lian</strong> （隶属：Mythic Talent）记录了 240 万人， <strong>Shintowai</strong> （独立）记录了 70 万人， <strong>Harris Caine</strong> （AKA Virtual）记录了 60 万人， <strong>Kurikoma Komaru</strong> （青桐高中）记录了 30 万人。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>本文介绍有关 VTuber 人才的信息以及每个机构、团体和公司的官方 YouTube 频道的订阅者数量。<strong>请注意，这些数据并不代表行业中每个人才、机构、团体或公司的规模或份额。</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> 12月29日为年末年初假期，因此我们发布12月23日至28日的汇总结果。感谢您的理解。</p></blockquote><p></p><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1"> 240万人</h2><h3 id="outline__1_1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1_1">菲莲</h3><figure class="wp-block-image"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="96320" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg?resize=1100%2C619&amp;ssl=1" alt="filia