</style><h3 id="outline__3" class="wp-block-heading">“ X Day”的任务</h3><h4 id="outline__3_1" class="wp-block-heading">WACTOR生产</h4><p>在就业环境方面，“看起来像人才和影响者”的意思是相同的。</p><p>今年早些时候，有关在Wactor Productions的拉丁美洲人才的雇用问题已经曝光。过去，过去有许多才华在过去不自然地工作，一些观众和粉丝的不信任和不满意，但是流行的人才Hinami Misora（Hina Misora）暂停了这项活动的暂停。他们达到顶峰。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Xw7yaS23bU"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/">Wactor Productions应该在拉丁美洲的观众和粉丝VTUBER VTUBER的系列赛中互相面对面</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Wactor Productions应该在拉丁美洲的观众和粉丝的Vtuber中互相面对” -P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/embed/#?secret=cpGdXanvrG#?secret=Xw7yaS23bU" data-secret="Xw7yaS23bU" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="7kR1Gpiaga"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-for-wactor-production-vtuber-hina-misora-and-tsukito-hana-released-a-statement/">Wactor Productions Vtuber Hinamisora Tsukitohana的前表演者 /语音模型发表了声明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“属于Wactor Productions的Vtuber Hinami Sora Tsukitohana的前表演者/语音模型，释放了一个声明”  -  P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-for-wactor-production-vtuber-hina-misora-and-tsukito-hana-released-a-statement/embed/#?secret=gM5zCatKQx#?secret=7kR1Gpiaga"